  "text": "Determination of body weight gain, food intake and energy intake Body weight change and food intake was measured according to method by Akase et al. [CITATION_1] . Intake of food was measured weekly on a cage basis and expressed as g of food/day. Initial body weight of all animals was measured before they were fed with either ND or HFD for 11 weeks. At the end of each week, the weight gain (%) was calculated as followed:",
